  "notes": "ap_invoices_all is the master header table for supplier invoices in Oracle EBS Accounts Payable module. It tracks invoice amount, type, vendor, and payment status. It integrates with AP invoice lines, payments, distributions, and GL accounting entries. Key invoice types: STANDARD, CREDIT, DEBIT, PREPAYMENT, AWT. Used to validate, approve, schedule, and pay invoices.",
